text.title: Vision & Mission
text.visionContent: Our vision is to be one of the best domestic shipping service companies committed to the development of human resources, network quantity and reliable operational systems.

children.missionOne: Committed to providing the best service to customers.
children.missionTwo: B Improve the company's performance continuously.
children.missionThree: To be the solution to the needs of domestic shipping services in the area.
children.missionFour: Play an active role in improving logistics knowledge and skills.
